## Overview

ZEDD is a scalable, enterprise-grade **AI-as-a-Service (SaaS)** platform designed to automate and enhance high-volume media workflows. By combining state-of-the-art generative AI with a robust asynchronous processing architecture, ZEDD enables users and businesses to transform images and videos at scale — through a unified API and a professional management dashboard.

ZEDD abstracts the complexity of high-resolution AI processing into a simple, reliable platform — from secure ingestion to asynchronous delivery — letting developers and creatives focus on building their core products.

