## Processing Workflow
```
1. Ingestion      — Assets are securely uploaded to integrated cloud storage
2. Orchestration  — Jobs are dispatched to the processing queue by priority
3. Inference      — Distributed workers execute specialized AI models
4. Verification   — Outputs are optimized and stored securely
5. Delivery       — Results delivered via secure endpoints with real-time notifications
```

---

## Scalability & Performance

- **Elastic Workers** — Processing capacity scales dynamically by adding worker nodes
- **Decoupled Architecture** — API components are isolated from compute tasks, preventing degradation during peak load
- **Intelligent Prioritization** — Advanced queueing ensures consistent performance across all user tiers
- **Automated Health Monitoring** — Continuous tracking for high availability and rapid task-level recovery

